des: This skill chooses from a selection of random facts concerning Norman the Bulldog. While some are fictional, others are not and are released with the expressed written consent of my dog. This is mainly just an app to learn about how Alexa skills are implemented.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
